    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "This 996.2 Carrera 4S is a superlative example of the wide-body 911 silhouette, powered by a rear-mounted 3.6L M96 flat-six utilizing VarioCam Plus timing. The engine\u2019s 315 hp is channeled through a 6-speed Getrag manual transaxle and a viscous-coupling AWD system, ensuring optimal torque distribution. Mechanically, this vehicle is turn-key; the IMS bearing has been addressed with a dual-row ceramic retrofit, and the rear main seal is dry. The chassis retains its factory-spec kinematics, with four-piston Brembo monoblock calipers clamping cross-drilled rotors for fade-free deceleration. Finished in concours-level paint with uniform depth readings, the cabin remains pristine with no bolster compression or UV degradation on the leather surfaces. A meticulously documented service history confirms its mechanical integrity.",
